{
  "stem": "24397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what the occasion was, but there was a marketplace near us, and they had the military there with ack-ack guns and searchlights and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, of course, all the kids went running up there and sat down on the equipment and were turning the handles and spinning around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was in amongst them doing exactly the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, not feeling any-- particularly any different, just doing what kids do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then-- but then gradually, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they stopped playing with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, it may have been because of their activity level was heightened because of all these things that they were involved in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so they-- I wasn't involved in any of that, so we--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was no way I could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being Jewish, I, I couldn't-- I wasn't allowed to be in any of these functions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if, if I-- anybody said to me, you can't come, or you're not-- I think this was something-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something was well, well-known to or made well-known to me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But then gradually they started shunning me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the difference between just not being part of it and being kind of ostracized from the-- what was going on around me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to the point that once, leaving school, a bunch of kids-- we were going through the park.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Vienna the parks are, are not like they seem to be in, in the States or in England where the grass is meant to be enjoyed underfoot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There you stick to the paved roads, and the grass is just to be looked at.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
